aors.data
Interface DataBusInterface

All Superinterfaces:
CollectionEventListener, CollectionInitEventListener, ControllerEventListener, java.util.EventListener, ObjektDestroyEventListener, ObjektInitEventListener, java.beans.PropertyChangeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
DataBus
public interface DataBusInterface
extends CollectionEventListener, java.beans.PropertyChangeListener, ObjektInitEventListener, CollectionInitEventListener, ObjektDestroyEventListener, ControllerEventListener

The DataBusInterface offers a reduced set of functions to the world. It will be used all over the simulator.

Since:
04/August/2009
